},{"pid":"661e31b518e4db519873c6e8d04a3acce7b6f999","tid":744864,"uid":142819,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會有啲鱷魚係度扮死  等待覆灼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af37c7015fc8c6eb4c5968c3f11bfcc293f562fe","tid":744864,"uid":33481,"like":5,"dislike":66,"score":-61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"完全唔明有咩問題"},{"pid":"3ef79881b62fb89f9328690b4c2e25a9789883f9","tid":744864,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":94,"score":-93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:43:07.000Z","msg":"估乜撚國家 第一個字就印尼"},{"pid":"12ab8ea2b1286a050c3b062cf1abef7f05e4bc88","tid":744864,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"估中咗，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0faef38553226991125373fad9d9df98328467b","tid":744864,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"afdfbcfc4ab00c0eee77543228562dae2a3b16c0","tid":744864,"uid":35717,"like":182,"dislike":5,"score":177,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"如果唔係流料D 村民都幾猛料<br />\n近三百條鱷魚， 用斧頭、棍棒及利刃就殺得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鱷魚甲咁厚要幾多棍先打得死， 比佢咬又死多幾個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:48:00.000Z","msg":"我都想像唔到點樣用棍打死鱷魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9188f2c05d3cdd280539e4630765449bf4183510","tid":744864,"uid":103156,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:48:48.000Z","msg":"One for all, all for one."},{"pid":"11e558e148cb8715dd9fc05301765f98bbbfb98b","tid":744864,"uid":155818,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n走去人地到殺哂全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cef264744bc01287d05ba4c045dbf9ac0abe21","tid":744864,"uid":5303,"like":15,"dislike":40,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:50:13.000Z","msg":"我希望係呢個post見唔到大愛左膠同動物撚"},{"pid":"d6e867ed4e95c87d2f5d6f90619228a1a698e9e7","tid":744864,"uid":9694,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"香港人去印尼姦左條女<br />\n咁係咪會集體黎姦番香港292個女人？痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8a8e98e4b91cfc0d3b17b6611a193cd97b0f4f","tid":744864,"uid":57035,"like":4,"dislike":41,"score":-37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:50:34.000Z","msg":"仲以為4，5米長嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有玩開運動嘅中學生都夠打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca4fd60c92f83e4ed1aef11f3f3bfec82ef1c31","tid":744864,"uid":111153,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"百位奉還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b33d7e6ccda271b7b97a587aeb2900984d4879","tid":744864,"uid":36029,"like":70,"dislike":5,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"661e31b518e4db519873c6e8d04a3acce7b6f999","tid":744864,"uid":142819,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會有啲鱷魚係度扮死  等待覆灼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"估國家？ 報復人類屠殺鱷魚 鱷魚群集體咬死292個人<br />\n<br />\n印尼發生屠殺人類慘案！一座位於印尼東部的小鎮，鱷魚群為了報復屠殺鱷魚的村民，竟然決定咬死早前在養殖場外居住的村民，數量高達292個。<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體報導，西巴布亞（West Papua）因鱷魚誤咬死人事件，一群村民拿著斧頭、棍棒及利刃，擅自衝進養殖場把所有292隻鱷魚全部殺光，結果屍體被堆成一堆，畫面相當驚人。其他附近的鱷魚上周六為他們舉行完喪禮後，決定要展開報復，一堆鱷魚紛紛伸出利牙及利爪，衝進養殖場外的部落把所有村民合共292個人全部殺光，屍體偏佈如山，畫面相當恐怖。<br />\n地方首領表示，這座養殖場外的部落村民擁有合法居留權，西巴布亞的原住部落已有一段長久的歷史。雖然先前的確是鱷魚咬死了人類，他們才繼而展開報復，此具對當地的養殖鱷魚形成了困擾，但其他鱷魚把所有村民全殺光，也實在令人無法接受。西巴布亞自然資源獵食首領馬努郎（Basar Manullang）說：「人類也是造物者賜與的生命，牠們也需要受到保護。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/180648_c56397e21edef422a99d281df0e7dd46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F180648_c56397e21edef422a99d281df0e7dd46.png&h=8364e045&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20143c8a30412c7d15faf4254a51b17b09960cf6","tid":744864,"uid":91362,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"印尼人正垃圾"},{"pid":"359917d53694cc3e4043ec469127fdb2b9e97e72","tid":744864,"uid":163031,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:38:32.000Z","msg":"擅自入去就要承受結果啦"},{"pid":"b36f86d2c7f79154ac3eecd537eefbaf8f982f93","tid":744864,"uid":67500,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"上帝創造人類管理地上一切走獸，是神默許的"},{"pid":"d59ea33e1836fc7b2d6d332a524d49c94222e40f","tid":744864,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T11:10:21.000Z","msg":"shithole country <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fe6c4bc3d16235947b20c99092b5383319cdcc","tid":744864,"uid":17928,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T11:28:50.000Z","msg":"斷人米路都幾撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19cd2d943e003afba45079a68b6b9ef0440b250","tid":744864,"uid":153963,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T11:31:47.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊係咪中國 點個係印尼<br />\n <br />\n但寧願相信係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0a90118043be684af570afa576ae9e933b139e","tid":744864,"uid":153963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T11:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲諗緊係咪中國 點知係印尼<br />\n <br />\n但寧願相信係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9ac88ce768e553489b64b0dc626147b119efe13e","