f630e93ddd4f4","tid":744864,"uid":162409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7bc2df860264ec7a1db06d27f6614269bd6468b","tid":744864,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"印尼發生屠殺鱷魚慘案！一座位於印尼東部的小鎮，村民為了報復咬死人的鱷魚，竟然決定殺死這隻鱷魚在養殖場的所有夥伴，數量高達292隻。<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體報導，西巴布亞（West Papua）一名48歲男子日前為了拔草餵牲畜，擅自進入一座鱷魚養殖場，結果被養殖場內的鱷魚攻擊狠咬，男子傷重不治死亡。村民上周六為他舉行完喪禮後，決定要展開報復，一堆人紛紛拿著斧頭、棍棒及利刃，衝進養殖場把所有292隻鱷魚全部殺光，屍體被堆成一堆，畫面相當驚人。<br />\n地方官員表示，這座養殖場擁有合法執照，專門養殖需要保護的淡水新幾內亞鱷。雖然發給執照的條件之一，是養殖場不得對附近社區居民形成困擾，但村民把鱷魚全殺光，也實在令人無法接受。西巴布亞自然資源保育局負責人馬努郎（Basar Manullang）說：「鱷魚也是造物者賜與的生命，牠們也需要受到保護。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180716/1392458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180716%2F1392458&d=nMFf4G2X1VZq%2Bl%2B5tUcDgTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6efc736e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180716%2F1392458&h=6219daa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180716/1392458</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180716/640_263f914cd64850f66959bcf796248ada.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180716%2F640_263f914cd64850f66959bcf796248ada.jpg&h=6347215f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"鱷魚沒有一條是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11012a4611fbb71d374cab44de44ddbd77ccc7a6","tid":744864,"uid":162409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:27:12.000Z","msg":"有無片  一定好睇過拍戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054b3f1d824e8c82a88dc618ac98d40264ebfd6c","tid":744864,"uid":159136,"like